item.description: Join us at this Dueling Piano Bar and start off 4th of July off with a bang. We will toast to July B-Days in our group(and June ones that just passed)These players are very funny&entertaining. So lets request our favorite songs&have some laughs..Admission is free and there are $5 appetizer specials. Turn in Brazis take a right/next lft in between warehouses plenty of parking!
